    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for explaining. i guess i'm mostly wondering about the \"traditional\" side you mentioned. a lot of parents i know are saying this kind of stuff is actually harmful or just inappropriate for kids. is there a scientific or logical basis for those concerns, or are they just based on old-fashioned ideas?",
